snippet.title: System Shock - Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2022
snippet.description: System Shock developer Nightdive Studios gave viewers a look at the flesh and steel fusion monsters of their ake on Citadel Station. System Shock is coming soon to PC, PlayStation and Xbox.
